name: Custom Design - anything you want!
description:
We can customize earrings, bracelets, pendants, and necklaces.  You customize with your color and gemstone preferences.  Feel free to send me an email at emilyjeanhabermehl@yahoo.com to inquire about a design before you order.  I will dialogue with you to make sure you're getting the piece you designed.  I will send a photo for your approval before anything is shipped.  All custom pieces are usually between $30 and $70 depending on the cost of supplies plus $4 shipping & handling.  You will be quoted a firm price before work begins.  

If you want to know exactly how much your piece will cost before ordering, email me.

Don't know exactly what you want?  No worries!  I can help you design a piece.  Just email me some basic ideas, favorite gemstones, favorite colors, etc. and we will work together.  You can also visit our Facebook page to get some ideas: facebook.com/emeraldcitycustom
